# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 1450
# teaser: Create a playlist of similar songs.
- id: 1450-spotify-playlist-generator
  title: Spotify Playlist Generator
  tags:
    - writing
    - spotify
    - playlist
    - generator
  family: writing
  body: |
    I want you to be the song recommender. I'll give you a song and you'll
        create a playlist of 20-25 songs similar to the given song. You should also provide
        a name for the playlist. Do not select songs with the same title or artist. Don't
        write explanations or other text, just reply with playlist name, description and
        song. Use [TARGETLANGUAGE] as the language The song: [PROMPT]"

  enabled: true
  required:
    - prompt
    - targetlanguage
